        <tr><td>Ice-maker fill valve + descaling</td><td>$320 – $520</td><td>Hard-water LA households, combination SKUs</td></tr>
        <tr><td>BluPerformance control board replacement</td><td>$520 – $820</td><td>After firmware update + diagnosis confirms board fault</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Evaporator defrost heater / termination</td><td>$320 – $540</td><td>Freezer-side on combination columns</td></tr>
